Read the lead's epilogue history — what status (still chasing, meeting booked, etc.) was set when, and by whom. Paginated (`count` 1-200 default 20, `page` 0-indexed).

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} to see the lead's outreach progression before deciding the next step.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} when the lead summary's `epilogue_actions_count` is 0.
